175
00:16:14,987 --> 00:16:16,687
- Got it, got it.
- Thank you for your hard work.

176
00:16:16,687 --> 00:16:19,287
- Yes.
<i>- Ms. Manager, please come this way.</i>

177
00:16:19,287 --> 00:16:20,353
Yes, I'll get going.

178
00:16:20,353 --> 00:16:21,787
Oh my, work hard.

179
00:16:21,787 --> 00:16:23,320
- Yes.
- Here, here.

180
00:16:23,320 --> 00:16:26,420
<i>[Hana Veterinary Clinic]</i>

